{
  "chapter": 31,
  "chapter_summary": "自动保底摘要：第31章围绕本章人物行止、冲突推进与场景转换展开。第三十一回半枚灵丹绝情谷占地甚广，群山围绕之中，方圆四万余亩。道路曲折，丘屏壑阻，杨过与小龙女展开轻身功夫，按图而行，片刻即到，见前面七八丈处数株大榆树交相覆荫，树底下是一座烧砖瓦的大窑，图中指明天竺僧和朱子柳便囚于此处。 黄蓉一直注视着绿萼的神色，只见她瞧着杨过的眼光之中流露出无限深情、无限焦虑，登时恍然，心道：\"蓉儿啊蓉儿，难道你做了妈妈，连女儿家的心事...",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "弓身走进窑门，跨步踏入，迎面一股热气扑到，听得有人喝道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 1,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨过道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 1,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 1,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你⋯⋯你⋯⋯",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 1,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那弟子知道谷主性命是他所救，曾当众说过要他作女婿，绿萼又和他交好，此人日后十九会当谷主，不敢得罪，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 1,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨过不理，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 1,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有朋自远方来，不亦乐乎？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师叔他老人家抗寒热的本领，本来远非我所能及，可是他⋯⋯",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那弟子奇道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "让开了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨兄弟，恭贺你武功大进！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "忙伸手探他鼻息，觉微有呼吸出入。朱子柳跟着从洞中跃出，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨过脸上一红，暗叫：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自知真正关心的其实并非天竺僧死活，而是自己妻子能否获救，问道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱子柳道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨过一惊，问道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨过和小龙女大奇，齐问：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱子柳叹道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是。不知他老人家何时能够醒转？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨过和小龙女对望一眼，均想：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们在这窑中，从那里找来的情花？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我二人给禁入火浣室中，有位年轻姑娘常来探望⋯⋯",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱子柳道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小龙女向杨过一笑，对朱子柳道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小龙女道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "尊师一灯大师也到了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨过眉头微皱，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱子柳奇道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨过也觉天竺僧的安危确是第一等大事，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱子柳沉吟道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "寻思半晌，总觉这绝情谷中处处诡秘，难觅稳妥的静养所在，心念一动，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱子柳伸手虚点一指，笑道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "抱起天竺僧，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小龙女道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "傻蛋到那儿去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "陆无双道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "心中也甚牵挂，突然道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "程英黯然道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "干么不用自己的剑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "跛足",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我便用别人的剑，领教领教你武功。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭芙道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说着向程英一指。郭芙以母亲之命，叫过程英一声",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "，心中早老大不服气，暗怪外公随随便便的收了这样一个幼徒，又想程英年纪和自己相若，未必有什么本领，这时给陆无双一顶，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "陆无双点点头，向郭芙道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有谁要冒充我爹爹妈妈的儿女？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你骂我是野种么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭大侠是忠厚长者，黄帮主是桃花岛主的亲女，他二位品德何等高超⋯⋯",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她只道陆无双真心颂扬她父母，剑招去势便缓了，那知陆无双接着道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭芙道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "陆无双阴阴的道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "陆无双向耶律齐瞪了一眼，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "耶律齐道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "陆无双抢着道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭芙满脸通红，按剑不语。耶律齐只得明言，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "转弯抹角，仍然骂她",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "见陆无双不住倒退，郭芙招招进逼，忽听得嗤的一声，陆无双裙子上划破了一道口子，跟着轻叫一声：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭芙提起剑来，见刃上有条血痕，知陆无双腿已受伤，得意洋洋的指着她道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "陆无双腿上创伤疼痛，怒道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天下人说什么了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "耶律齐道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭芙急道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她见程英美貌淡雅，风姿嫣然，突然动念：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "耶律齐半点也没猜到她念头，续道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这四句话每一句都刺中了郭芙的心事，她心头一震，问道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "陆无双冷笑道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "玉漏催银箭",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "弹指神通",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "陆无双回头笑道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭芙恨恨的道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "耶律齐",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
