      "line_end": 731
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他两个说些什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 712,
      "line_end": 731
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫哭，莫哭！后来怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 712,
      "line_end": 731
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "绿萼出了一身冷汗，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 732,
      "line_end": 759
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "裘千尺道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 732,
      "line_end": 759
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "绿萼灵机一动，咬牙道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 732,
      "line_end": 759
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妈，女儿这番是活不成了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 732,
      "line_end": 759
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "绿萼道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 732,
      "line_end": 759
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "裘千尺暗自沉吟：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 760,
      "line_end": 779
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 760,
      "line_end": 779
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们取绝情丹去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 760,
      "line_end": 779
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "裘千尺哼了一声，心道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 780,
      "line_end": 803
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沉声道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 780,
      "line_end": 803
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉微笑道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 780,
      "line_end": 803
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "裘千尺心中一凛，暗想：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 780,
      "line_end": 803
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "冷冷的道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 780,
      "line_end": 803
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉这般说，可让对方占尽了便宜，裘千尺除枣核钉厉害之外别无伤敌手段，而大声说出",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 804,
      "line_end": 829
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当真有这么好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 804,
      "line_end": 829
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉微笑道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 804,
      "line_end": 829
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭芙叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 804,
      "line_end": 829
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "裘千尺向众弟子扫射了一眼，心想：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 830,
      "line_end": 853
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有恩不报，岂不与禽兽无异",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 830,
      "line_end": 853
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但这念头便如闪电般一瞬即过，善念消退，恶心立生，冷冷的道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 830,
      "line_end": 853
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说着纵身退后，站在大厅正中，与裘千尺相距约莫三丈，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 854,
      "line_end": 883
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉微微一笑，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 854,
      "line_end": 883
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各人闪⋯⋯",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 854,
      "line_end": 883
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "开",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 854,
      "line_end": 883
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 854,
      "line_end": 883
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不避不格",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 884,
      "line_end": 901
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但自己亲口答应给药，言入众人之耳，总不能立时反悔，她双眼一转，已有计较，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 902,
      "line_end": 923
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "转头向黄蓉道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 924,
      "line_end": 955
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "点头说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 924,
      "line_end": 955
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
